subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: When the Chase for the Nextel Cup playoff begins Sunday at New Hampshire, 7 of the 10 drivers who competed for the Cup last season will be ineligible this year.
